\begin{itemize}
    \item Reduce teaching hours from 9am-6pm to 9am-5pm
    \item Encourage a lunch break between for students with more than 4 hours of classes a/per day?
    \item Minimise clashes, including optional courses
    \item Improve room usage and reduce idle capacity
\end{itemize}
