\begin{frame}{Our Approach}
\textbf{Our Approach}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Formulate the problem as an integer programming model
    \item Use Gurobi to solve the optimisation problem
    \item Test first on the Vet School subset
    \item Extend to the broader university dataset
